  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个健康科技EMR同步模块的状态流转图。核心场景是：系统从空闲状态开始，发起请求后进入加载，然后根据结果走向成功或错误，最后都能回到空闲。不过错误分支还要支持中止到患者记录模块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "Idle",
        "Loading",
        "Success",
        "Error",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我确认一下结构：起点是EMR同步模块，然后到Idle空闲态。从Idle到Loading的触发条件是\"Start Request\"对吗？另外Error到患者记录这条线，标签用\"Abort\"是否准确？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Loading",
        "Start Request",
        "Error",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "Abort"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Idle收到Start Request就进入Loading。Abort这个标签可以，表示用户选择放弃同步、转去查看患者记录。还有Success和Error都要能回到Idle，Success用\"Reset\"，Error用\"Retry\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Loading",
        "Success",
        "Error",
        "Idle",
        "Reset",
        "Retry"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先用stateDiagram-v2把主框架搭出来：EMR同步指向Idle，Idle到Loading标注Start Request，Loading分出两条线到Success和Error，分别对应Data Received和Request Failed。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "Idle",
        "Loading",
        "Success",
        "Error",
        "Start Request",
        "Data Received",
        "Request Failed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Loading到Success的条件再明确一下，应该是\"Data Received\"，失败则是\"Request Failed\"。另外Success回Idle的Reset和Error回Idle的Retry这两条反向流转别忘了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Loading",
        "Success",
        "Error",
        "Idle",
        "Data Received",
        "Request Failed",
        "Reset",
        "Retry"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已加上：Success通过Reset回到Idle，Error通过Retry也回到Idle。现在还剩Error到患者记录的中止分支，我标注为Abort。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Success",
        "Idle",
        "Reset",
        "Error",
        "Retry",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "Abort"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
